stin prwti askisi kanw stin main dimiourgw ta threads west kai east
ama erthoun pollapla west kai meta ena east ektelw ta west prosexontas
na ektelountai tria tria enw kanw wait stin main prin dimiourgisei to east
wste otan teleiwsoun ta west kai einai eleutheros o dromos na paroun 
prwtaireotita ta east.

stin deuteri dimiourgw ola ta cars mazi kai ta bazw na exoun tixaio xrono epibibasis 
ama to ferry gemisei tote to ksipnaw pigene adeiazei ta autokinita girnaei kai meta anoigei
tis theseis tou gia to epomeno load kai peftei pali se sleep. otan den tha exw alla autokinita
na perimenoun tote ksipnaw gia mia teleutaia fora to ferry to opoio otan girisei kanei elegxo ama teleiwsan
kai kanei exit